Citation.sTitle: Densities and Isothermal Compressibilities at Pressures up to 20 MPa of the Systems N,N-Dimethylformamide or N,N-Dimethylacetamide + 1-Chloroalkane
Citation.sAbstract: Densities of N,N-dimethylformamide or N,N-dimethylacetamide + 1-chlorobutane, or + 1-chlorohexane, or + 1-chlorooctane at 298.15 K and at pressures up to 20 MPa have been measured. Isothermal compressibilities of the pure liquids and their mixtures were obtained.
